ort to actively manage and monitor asset allocations not only through the qualitative process of ongoing dialogue with managers but also by utilizing rigorous quantitative measures risk management is handled by a team of portfolio risk and operational risk professionals who are independent of the research team “the most rewarding aspect of what we do is developing strong longterm relationships with our clients at the end of the day that is how we define our success” geoffrey lewis managing director and cfo xmllangenus langenus xmlnshttpwwwworgxhtml investmentprocess registration client login english 〔〕 français españolas deutsch italiano  한국어 home our firm overview why optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire our programs investment program investment process proprietary platform our team contact us accueil notre société vue densemble pourquoi optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire nos programmes programme dinvestissement processus dinvestissement plateforme exclusive notre équipe nous contacter home unsere firma übersicht warum optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire unsere programme investitionsprogramm investment process proprietäre plattform unser team kontakt inicio nuestra firma panorama por qué optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire nuestros programas programa de inversiones proceso de inversión plataforma de propiedad nuestro equipo contactenos home   なぜoptima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire たちのプログラム  プロセス のプラットフォーム 達のチーム おいわせ home la nostra società chi siamo perché optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire i nostri prodotti prodotti di investimento processo di investimento piattaforma tecnologica la nostra squadra contatti     optima th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire       홈 회사소개 개요 optima는 왜 th anniversary letter hedge magazine interview with dixon boardman dixon boardman profile in citywire 저희 투자 프로그램 투자 프로그램 투자 프로세스 자체 플렛폼 저희 팀 문의하기 disciplined investment process the investment process for our multimanager portfolios is rigorous disciplined and consistent it combines a topdown macroeconomic view with bottomup fundamental research performed by the investment and operations teams – all of which is supported by the firm’s proprietary manager analysis and research system operas optima’s fourstep investment process includes macroasset allocation is the product of our investment outlook which is based on the analysis of macroeconomic data and other factors that impact the major geographic regions and hedge fund strategies in which we invest key data inputs are formally reviewed by the research department on a quarterly basis resulting in a baseline outlook and asset allocations are then adjusted as appropriate manager selection is conducted through a systematic threestage process which incorporates both qualitative and quantitative analyses prior to funding any manager a detailed investment book based upon the findings of the due diligence process is finalized bound and signed by the cio cfochief operations risk officer chief portfolio risk officer and general counsel portfolio construction similarly integrates both qualitative and quantitative elements in constructing portfolios from optima’s list of managers approved for investment an investment is made and sized based on factors including correlations liquidity exposures and diversification risk management efforts are forward looking and aim to identify problems early enough to take preemptive action before substantial losses are incurred the team is divided between specialists in portfolio risk and operational risk the evaluation of risk is central to determining whether a manager is approved for investment and the risk team has the right to veto any manager unable to meet optima’s strict standards   “we evaluate numerous managers across a broad spectrum of strategies only those we deem ‘bestinclass’ qualify for our singlemanager funds” michael spelman managing director optima fund management lp  new york  ny  company information products resources my account talk to a db advisor  business directory ny new york management investment openend management investment openend optima fund management lp o optima fund management lp claim this business  e rd st fl  new york ny  get directions   wwwoptimacom business info founded  incorporated annual revenue  employee count  industries management investment openend contacts dixon boardman contact business your email address subject message send message company summary since  the company has been providing management investment openend verified status verified address unverified last verified      phone unverified payment method verified view full report similar businesses nearby our similar businesses nearby shows similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review profile competitive landscape our competitive landscape shows how this business compares to similar businesses in their industry and region based on information found in their dun  bradstreet credibility review profile payments accepted no data hours sunday   monday   tuesday   wednesday   thursday   friday   saturday   o view additional data select from over  networks below to view available data about this business if this data is unavailable or inaccurate and you own or represent this business click here for more information on how you may be able to correct it credibility review google facebookcom yellowbookcom bingcom yellowpagescom merchantcircle tele atlas tomtom twittercom aol mapq